Video Assistant Referee (VAR) continues to generate controversies especially in the English Premier League (EPL) and there have been calls for it to be removed. TV Independent on TVI ‘Street Voice’ asked football-loving Nigerians about this important issue. Leave your thoughts in the comment section. —
